<num value="1">一</num>人</measure>
<pc>，</pc>折戶婚之訟<pc>，</pc>而通書<num value="6">六</num>曹之案牒<pc>。</pc>功曹<pc>、</pc>倉曹<pc>、</pc>戶曹<pc>、</pc>兵曹<pc>、</pc>法曹<pc>、</pc>士曹參軍各<measure quantity="1" unit="people">
