</div>
<div>
<p>開封典司轂下<pc>，</pc>自<date notBefore="960" notAfter="963">建隆</date>以來<pc>，</pc>為要劇之任<pc>。</pc>至<date notBefore="1068" notAfter="1077">熙寧</date>間<pc>，</pc>增給吏錄<pc>，</pc>禁其受賕<pc>，</pc>省衙前役以寬民力<pc>，</pc>厘折獄訟歸於廂官<pc>，</pc>而治事視前日損去<num value="14">十四</num>
<pc>。</pc>
<date notBefore="1086" notAfter="1094">元祐</date>元年<pc>，</pc>詔府界捕盜官吏隸本府<pc>，</pc>與都大提舉司同管轄而掌其賞罰<pc>。</pc>置新城內左<pc>、</pc>右<num value="2">二</num>廂<pc>。</pc>
<measure quantity="3" unit="years">
<num value="3">三</num>年</measure>
<pc>，</pc>以罷大理寺獄<pc>，</pc>置軍巡院判官<num value="1">一</num>員<pc>。</pc>
<measure quantity="4" unit="years">
